Tittle:- Design a web page that includes an image, hyperlink, and a nested table.
Program-   


<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head> 
<title>Image, Hyperlink and Nested Table</title> 
</head> 
<body> 
<h1>My Web Page</h1> 
<!-- Image --> 
<h2>Image</h2> 
<img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.dfrEuADXOvFJIynklEAoagHaEK?o=7rm=3&rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3" alt="Sample Image" width="200" height="150"> 
<!-- Hyperlink --> 
<h2>Hyperlink</h2> 
<a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">Click here to visit Google</a> 
<!-- Table with Nested Table --> 
<h2>Table with Nested Table</h2> 
<table border="1" cellpadding="5"> 
<tr> 
<th>Name</th> 
<th>Details</th> 
</tr> 
<tr> 
<td>Amit</td> 
<td> 
<table border="1" cellpadding="5"> 
<tr> 
<th>Subject</th> 
<th>Marks</th> 
</tr> 
<tr> 
<td>Maths</td> 
<td>80</td> 
</tr> 
<tr> 
<td>Science</td> 
<td>85</td> 
</tr> 
</table> 
</td> 
</tr> 
</table> 
</body> 
</html>

